</style></head> <body> <a href="/" class="back">&larr; Back to posts</a> <h1>Astro Meets Firestore: Building a CMS-Powered Blog</h1> <p class="meta"> March 10, 2024 </p> <div class="tags"> <span class="tag">Astro</span><span class="tag">Firebase</span> </div> <div class="content"> <h1 id="astro-meets-firestore">Astro Meets Firestore</h1>
<p>Combine Astro’s Content Layer API with Firestore for a powerful CMS experience.</p>
<h2 id="the-stack">The Stack</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Astro</strong> for the frontend</li>
<li><strong>Firestore</strong> for the data layer</li>
