<p>Astro is a modern web framework for building fast, content-driven websites.</p>
<h2 id="why-astro">Why Astro?</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Fast by default</strong> — Zero JS shipped to the browser</li>
<li><strong>Content-focused</strong> — Built for content-rich websites</li>
<li><strong>Island architecture</strong> — Interactive components only where needed</li>
</ul> </div> </body></html>"
